Interface DataElementInterface

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
CaDSRDE, DataElement, UserDefinedDE
public interface DataElementInterface

Data element represent the source of the permissible values for a primitive attribute. Data element is an abstract class.The data element may be of type caDSRDE or of type user defined.
